===Etymology===
{{Han compound|扌|戈|c1=s|c2=p|ls=psc}}

Originally a variant form of [[划]].  Borrowed to mean a similar action.

The popular interpretation as a hand [[扌]] looking for an halberd [[戈]] is a [[mnemonic]] and not an etymology.

